eBay,Return,Management,API,lets,developers,to,retrieve,and,manage,buyer,returns,Information,retrieved,can,be,a,summary,of,a,buyer,s,return,items,or,detailed,information,about,their,specific,returns,Some,of,these,detailed,information,includes,reasons,for,the,return,days,allowed,for,returns,Additionally,this,API,also,allows,developers,to,provide,buyers,with,return,information